ðŸ”§ Delegate OU Permissions

1.	In Active Directory Users and Computers, right-click the OU (e.g., IT).
2.	Select Delegate Control.
3.	Choose the user/group to delegate.
4.	Choose common tasks or custom task â†’ allow permissions like:
o	Reset user passwords
o	Create/delete user accounts

ðŸ›‘ View Delegation
