ðŸ”— 10ï¸âƒ£ Domain & Forest Trusts
________________________________________
ðŸ“ Create Trusts

Trusts require at least 2 domains/forests. Example: vlab.local & corp.local
1.	Open Active Directory Domains and Trusts.
2.	Right-click your domain â†’ Properties â†’ Trusts â†’ New Trust.
3.	Enter the name of the other domain.
4.	Choose trust type:
o	External Trust
o	Forest Trust
o	Shortcut Trust
5.	Choose direction:
o	One-way: Incoming or Outgoing
o	Two-way

ðŸ”„ Verify Trusts
nltest /domain_trusts
